UI is split in 2 tabs: Trajectory Generation and System Identification
Sysid has a video where users go through frame-by-frame and plot positions of ball.
when users first upload video popup appears (called setup popup) 
There is sim overlay so they can fit drag and magnus coefficients.
Traj gen generates trajectories using drag and magnus coefficients.
Each UI tab has a left and right panel.
Sysid left panel has 2 tabs: upload/save and traj labeling
Sysid right panel has a sim section where users specify simulation overly
Traj Gen left panel has parameters to generate trajectories
Traj Gen right panel shows a list of generated trajectories as well as utility functions to manage and save trajectories